      "comment": "BEEJAYS STAR (8) made a good start for this yard when she placed first up at this circuit and distance then drew wider on this row when midfield last time. Should enjoy a trail and will be nearing her peak. ASCOT SHOWTIME (1) made it two wins from her last three starts when she led from a couple of spots wider and scored by close to 10 metres here last time. Taking on a better field but she can take advantage of the inside draw. Former Victorian GOODOLBOYSANDBEER (2) is another that is fitter for recent racing and has yet to finish worse than fourth this time in, coming from wider to place last week. Should enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position. LETS GO BAILEY (9) may need some luck from the back row but did a good job to win here two back.",
